		<paragraph x="12" y="+4" width="605" height="0" style="headline" tabs="0" indent="0"><![CDATA[<B><TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="12" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0"><B>The table shows marriage and divorce statistics in the UK between 1971 and 1999, while the line graph shows how the number of children with divorced parents varied over approximately the same period in England and Wales. </B></FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT></B>]]></paragraph>
